<h2 class="bold font-l">Anne and Sasha ditch school</h2>
<p class="_pmvv-vidbox-descTxt">
Sasha convinces Anne to ditch school for her birthday, a sign of her controlling attitude and the bad influence she gives her. </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
